## Task 1 – Digital Literacy Infographic

In this task, I created an infographic to explain the concept of **digital literacy** and its importance in today’s digital world. The infographic highlights key topics such as safe internet practices, maintaining a professional online presence, and proper email etiquette. The objective of this task was to present these ideas in a clear and visually engaging format so that they can be easily understood by a wider audience. The infographic was designed using Canva.

